quantum systems, while the time-independent form gives us

101
00:06:19,274 --> 00:06:23,901
energy eigenvalues and eigenstates. The probabilistic interpretation connects

102
00:06:24,001 --> 00:06:27,277
abstract mathematics to measurable physical quantities.

103
00:06:27,366 --> 00:06:31,058
As you continue your journey in quantum mechanics, remember that the

104
00:06:31,158 --> 00:06:35,407
Schrödinger equation is your primary tool for understanding the quantum world.

105
00:06:35,507 --> 00:06:39,868
From atoms to materials to quantum technologies, this elegant equation continues

